HEADWORD: Cyanotic
<hw>Cy`a*not"ic</hw> <pr>(s?`?-n?t"?k)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Relating to cyanosis; affected with cyanosis;
